        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Fields:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>mux [ 0 : 2 ] - Multiplexing function (3 bits)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>pin [ 3 : 6 ] - Pin number (4 bits, 0-15)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>port [ 7 : 7 ] - Port identifier (1 bit, 0=PA, 1=PB)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
